#

Tofu and Quinoa Salad

35 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

HealthyQuickSalad

Description

A light and refreshing salad packed with protein and nutrients, perfect for a quick lunch or dinner!

Ingredients

  • quinoa: 1 cup
  • firm tofu: 1 block (14 oz)
  • bell pepper: 1 (any color)
  • cucumber: 1
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • soy sauce: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup (chopped)
